<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> فَاتَهُ الحَجُّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَتَحَلَّلَ بِعُمْرَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا تُجْزِئُ عَنْ عُمْرَةِ الإِسْلَامِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَهَدْيٌ إِنْ لَمْ يَكُنِ اشْتَرَطَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَقَضَى مِنَ العَامِ القَابِلِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَمَنْ مُنِعَ البَيْتَ -وَلَوْ بَعْدَ الوُقُوفِ أَوْ فِي عُمْرَةٍ-:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- ذَبَحَ هَدْيًا بِنِيَّةِ التَّحَلُّلِ وُجُوبًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- فَإِنْ لَمْ يَجِدْ صَامَ عَشَرَةَ أَيَّامٍ بِالنِّيَّةِ وَحَلَّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَلَا إِطْعَامَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمَنْ صُدَّ عَنْ عَرَفَةَ فِي حَجٍّ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- تَحَلَّلَ بِعُمْرَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَلَا دَمَ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>